===[[Etymology]]===
:Greek ''amethystos'', meaning "not drunken". The Greeks believed that the amethyst prevented intoxication.
===[[noun]]===
#a transparent purple variety of [[quartz]], used as a [[gemstone]].
#a [[purple]] [[colour]].
